<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/midterm.css">
    <script src="index.js"></script>
    <title>Document</title>
    <link 
    href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" 
    rel="stylesheet" 
    integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" 
    crossorigin="anonymous"> <!--created this file in advance for bootstrap just to make it easier to get started.-->
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container-fluid background">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 flayer"> 
                <div class="transparent">you see nothing</div>
            </div>
        </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <div class="displaybar">
                            <p>Home        about        Catagories        Contact</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-2 transparent"> spacer </div>
                <div class="col-md-8 testcolor">
                    <div class="title">
                            Move CPTS 489 to Afternoon in Winter!
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-7 text">
                            <p>The image you see to the right represents our teacher absolutely chilling from the extreme
                                cold weather out there! please sight this patition at the bottom to support our move to an Afternoon
                                class schedule. 
                                The image you see on the right is a representation of our professor every morning, 
                                right before his much-needed coffee that helps thaw him out a bit. Imagine having 
                                to wake up at 4 or 5 AM in the dead of winter just to prepare for class. Technically, 
                                since the sun hasnâ€™t even risen yet, can we really call 4 AM "morning"? The frigid cold, 
                                combined with the mental fog of early hours, is an unfair battle both for students and faculty
                                 alike. No one should have to endure sub-zero temperatures just to attend an 8 AM lecture. 
                                 Morning brain freeze inevitably leads to null pointer exceptions in our heads! For these
                                reasons, we humbly 
                                request the administration to consider shifting CPTS 489 to a more humane
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-1 image">
                            <image class="img" src="images/s-l400-2.jpg" alt=""/>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="petition">Fill out Form!</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row pcenter">
                        <form name="myForm" action="/submit" method="POST" onsubmit="return validateInput()"> 
                            <fieldset legend="Login">
                                <div>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <label  class="first_n" for="first_n"> First Name: </label>
                                    <input type="text" id="first_n" name="first_n" placeholder="first name" required/>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <label class="last_n" for="last_n"> Last Name:</label>
                                    <input type="text" id="last_n" name="last_n" placeholder="last name" required/>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <label class="gender" for="gender"> Gender:</label>
                                    <select id="gender" name="gender">
                                    <option value="">--select--</option>
                                    <option>Male</option>
                                    <option>Female</option>
                                    <option>Other</option>
                                    </select>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <label class="age" for="age"> Age:</label>
                                    <input type="number" id="age" name="age" min = "0" placeholder="age" required/>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <label class="fpl" for="fpl"> Favorite Programming language:</label>
                                    <select id="fpl" name="fpl">
                                    <option value="">--select--</option>
                                    <option>Python</option>
                                    <option>Java</option>
                                    <option>C++</option>
                                    <option>C</option>
                                    <option>lua</option>
                                    </select required>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <label class="ides" for="ides"> Integrated Development Environment:</label>
                                    <select id="ides" name="ides">
                                    <option value="">--select--</option>
                                    <option>Visual Studio Code</option>
                                    <option>IntelliJ IDEA</option>
                                    <option>Sublime Text</option>
                                    <option>Visual Studio Community</option>
                                    </select>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <label class="muf" for="muf">Most frequently used Frameworks/Libraries </label>
                                    <select id="muf" name="muf">
                                    <option value="">--select--</option>
                                    <option>React</option>
                                    <option>Angular</option>
                                    <option>Django</option>
                                    <option>Express</option>
                                    <option>Other</option>
                                    </select>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <label class="vc" for="state">Version Control</label>
                                    <select id="vc" name="vc">
                                    <option value="">--select--</option>
                                    <option>Git</option>
                                    <option>SVN (Subversion)</option>
                                    <option>Mercurial</option>
                                    <option>Another</option>
                                    </select>
                                </div>
                                <script>
                                    function submission() {
                                      alert("Submission complete");
                                    }
                                </script>
                                <div>
                                    <button class="button" onclick="submission">Submit survey</button> 
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row"> 
                                <table>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>First Name</th>
                                        <th>Last Name</th>
                                        <th>Gender</th>
                                        <th>Age</th>
                                        <th>IDE</th>
                                        <th>Favorite Programming language</th>
                                        <th>Most Frequent Libraries</th>
                                        <th>Version Control</th>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tbody>
                                      <% table_data.forEach((row) => {%>
                                      <tr>
                                        <td class="telem"><%= row.first_n %></td>
                                        <td class="telem"><%= row.last_n %></td>
                                        <td class="telem"><%= row.gender %></td>
                                        <td class="telem"><%= row.age %></td>
                                        <td class="telem"><%= row.ides %></td>
                                        <td class="telem"><%= row.fpl %></td>
                                        <td class="telem"><%= row.muf %></td>
                                        <td class="telem"><%= row.vc %></td>
                                      <!-- create the rest of these to add name, city, and state -->
                                      </tr>
                                      <% }) %>
                                    </tbody>
                                </table>
                               
                            </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
    <script 
src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" 
integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" 
crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>


